text.section:
A building requirement adopted under this section:
shall be imposed for:
the protection of the public health, safety, and welfare; or
the preservation, improvement, or protection of lands, water, and improvements in the municipal corporation or governed special taxing district; and
may regulate only the construction, repair, or remodeling of single-family residential houses or buildings on land zoned for single-family residential use as it relates to:
fences, walls, hedges, and similar barriers;
signs;
residential parking;
residential storage;
the location of structures, including setback requirements;
the dimensions of structures, including height, bulk, massing, and design; and
lot coverage, including impervious surfaces.
